17．循環小数を分数で表す【改訂版　STEP演習　中学数学３　STEP B　問題17】  
次の循環小数を分数で表しなさい。  
(1) 0.\overline{8} (2) 0.\overline{79} (3) 0.\overline{345} (4) 3.9\overline{7}  

解答  
(1)\; rac{{8}}{{9}} (2)\; rac{{79}}{{99}} (3)\; rac{{115}}{{333}} (4)\; rac{{179}}{{45}}  

(1) x = 0.\overline{8} とおくと  
 10x = 8.\overline{8}  
10x − x を計算すると 9x = 8  
よって  
 x =  rac{{8}}{{9}}  
答  rac{{8}}{{9}}  

(2) x = 0.\overline{79} とおくと  
 100x = 79.\overline{79}  
100x − x を計算すると 99x = 79  
よって  
 x =  rac{{79}}{{99}}  
答  rac{{79}}{{99}}  

(3) x = 0.\overline{345} とおくと  
 1000x = 345.\overline{345}  
1000x − x を計算すると 999x = 345  
よって  
 x =  rac{{345}}{{999}} =  rac{{115}}{{333}}  
答  rac{{115}}{{333}}  

(4) x = 3.9\overline{7} とおくと  
 10x = 39.\overline{7}  
 100x = 397.\overline{7}  
100x − 10x を計算すると 90x = 358  
よって  
 x =  rac{{358}}{{90}} =  rac{{179}}{{45}}  
答  rac{{179}}{{45}}

18. 平方根の乗法［改訂版 STEP演習 中学数学３ STEP A 問題18］  
次の計算をしなさい。  
(1) √2 × √3 (2) √3 × √11 (3) √5 × √13  
(4) √8 × √2 (5) √2 × (−√7) (6) (−√17) × (−√3)  
(7) √21 × √(5/7) (8) √(5/12) × √(24/5) (9) √28 × √0.5  

解答  
(1) √6 (2) √33 (3) √65 (4) 4 (5) −√14 (6) √51  
(7) √15 (8) √2 (9) √14  

(1)  
\sqrt{2}	imes\sqrt{3}=\sqrt{2	imes3}=\sqrt{6}  

(2)  
\sqrt{3}	imes\sqrt{11}=\sqrt{3	imes11}=\sqrt{33}  

(3)  
\sqrt{5}	imes\sqrt{13}=\sqrt{5	imes13}=\sqrt{65}  

(4)  
\sqrt{8}	imes\sqrt{2}=\sqrt{8	imes2}=\sqrt{4^{2}}=4  

(5)  
\sqrt{2}	imes igl(-\sqrt{7} igr)=-\sqrt{2	imes7}=-\sqrt{14}  

(6)  
 igl(-\sqrt{17} igr)	imes igl(-\sqrt{3} igr)=\sqrt{17	imes3}=\sqrt{51}  

(7)  
\sqrt{21}	imes\sqrt{ rac{{5}}{{7}}}
=\sqrt{21	imes rac{{5}}{{7}}}
=\sqrt{15}  

(8)  
\sqrt{ rac{{5}}{{12}}}	imes\sqrt{ rac{{24}}{{5}}}
=\sqrt{ rac{{5}}{{12}}	imes rac{{24}}{{5}}}
=\sqrt{2}  

(9)  
\sqrt{28}	imes\sqrt{0.5}=\sqrt{28	imes0.5}=\sqrt{14}

19. 平方根の除法[改訂版 STEP演習 中学数学3 STEP A 問題19]  
次の計算をしなさい。  
(1)  rac{\sqrt{14}}{\sqrt{2}} (2)  rac{\sqrt{48}}{\sqrt{8}} (3)  rac{\sqrt{85}}{\sqrt{5}} (4)  rac{\sqrt{108}}{\sqrt{3}} (5) - rac{\sqrt{42}}{\sqrt{14}}

解答  
(1) \sqrt{7}  
(2) \sqrt{6}  
(3) \sqrt{17}  
(4) 6  
(5) -\sqrt{3}

(1)  rac{\sqrt{14}}{\sqrt{2}} = \sqrt{ rac{{14}}{{2}}} = \sqrt{7}  
(2)  rac{\sqrt{48}}{\sqrt{8}} = \sqrt{ rac{{48}}{{8}}} = \sqrt{6}  
(3)  rac{\sqrt{85}}{\sqrt{5}} = \sqrt{ rac{{85}}{{5}}} = \sqrt{17}  
(4)  rac{\sqrt{108}}{\sqrt{3}} = \sqrt{ rac{{108}}{{3}}} = \sqrt{36} = \sqrt{6^2} = 6  
(5) -\, rac{\sqrt{42}}{\sqrt{14}} = -\sqrt{ rac{{42}}{{14}}} = -\sqrt{3}

20. 平方根の除法［改訂版 STEP演習 中学数学3 STEP A 問題20］  
次の計算をしなさい。  
(1) \sqrt{24} \div \sqrt{12}  
(2) \sqrt{65} \div \sqrt{13}  
(3) \sqrt{225} \div \sqrt{15}  
(4) \sqrt{18} \div \sqrt{2}  
(5) (−\sqrt{35}) \div \sqrt{7}  
(6) (−\sqrt{52}) \div (−\sqrt{13})  

解答  
(1) \sqrt{2}  (2) \sqrt{5}  (3) \sqrt{15}  (4) 3  (5) −\sqrt{5}  (6) 2  

(1) \sqrt{24} \div \sqrt{12}  
    =  rac{{\sqrt{24}}}{{\sqrt{12}}}  
    = \sqrt{ rac{{24}}{{12}}}  
    = \sqrt{2}  

(2) \sqrt{65} \div \sqrt{13}  
    =  rac{{\sqrt{65}}}{{\sqrt{13}}}  
    = \sqrt{ rac{{65}}{{13}}}  
    = \sqrt{5}  

(3) \sqrt{225} \div \sqrt{15}  
    =  rac{{\sqrt{225}}}{{\sqrt{15}}}  
    = \sqrt{ rac{{225}}{{15}}}  
    = \sqrt{15}  

(4) \sqrt{18} \div \sqrt{2}  
    =  rac{{\sqrt{18}}}{{\sqrt{2}}}  
    = \sqrt{ rac{{18}}{{2}}}  
    = \sqrt{9}  
    = 3  

(5) (−\sqrt{35}) \div \sqrt{7}  
    = − rac{{\sqrt{35}}}{{\sqrt{7}}}  
    = −\sqrt{ rac{{35}}{{7}}}  
    = −\sqrt{5}  

(6) (−\sqrt{52}) \div (−\sqrt{13})  
    =  rac{{\sqrt{52}}}{{\sqrt{13}}}  
    = \sqrt{ rac{{52}}{{13}}}  
    = \sqrt{4}  
    = 2

25. 平方根の乗法［改訂版　STEP演習　中学数学3　STEP A　問題25］  
次の計算をしなさい。  
(1) \sqrt{8} 	imes \sqrt{45}  
(2) \sqrt{28} 	imes \sqrt{75}  
(3) -\sqrt{12} 	imes \sqrt{18}  
