x^2−x+\left( rac{{1}}{{2}}ight)^2 = 3+\left( rac{{1}}{{2}}ight)^2  
\left(x− rac{{1}}{{2}}ight)^2 =  rac{{13}}{{4}}  
x− rac{{1}}{{2}} = \pm  rac{{\sqrt{13}}}{{2}}  
よって x =  rac{{1 \pm \sqrt{13}}}{{2}}  

(3)  x^2−5x+1=0  
